---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon';
import { Picture } from '@astrojs/image/components'
---

<section class="px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 mx-auto lg:px-8 lg:py-20 max-w-6xl">
	<div class="grid gap-6 row-gap-10 md:grid-cols-2">
		<div class="md:pb-6 md:pr-16">
			<h2 class="mb-8 text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold font-heading">
				I'm currently taking the Google Data Analyst Certificate
			</h2>
			<div class="flex">
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-4">
					<div>
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-primary-600 border-2">
							<Icon name="tabler:arrow-down" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-slate-200" />
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="w-px h-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-slate-500"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="pt-1 pb-8">
					<p class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-300">Step 1</p>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
						Given a business task, question or a problem observed in the world, the first step is to gather the data and tools needed.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="flex">
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-4">
					<div>
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-primary-600 border-2">
							<Icon name="tabler:arrow-down" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-slate-200" />
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="w-px h-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-slate-500"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="pt-1 pb-8">
					<p class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-300">Step 2</p>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
						Storing the data in a spreadsheet or database, we can then organize and pre-process the data for further analysis. 
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="flex">
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-4">
					<div>
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-primary-600 border-2">
							<Icon name="tabler:arrow-down" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-slate-200" />
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="w-px h-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-slate-500"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="pt-1 pb-8">
					<p class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-300">Step 3</p>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
						Visualize the results using tables, graphs or charts so as to present the stakholders with business insights derived from the data analysis. Although this may be simplification of the process, I believe it all boils down to these overall steps.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="flex">
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-4">
					<div>
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-primary-600 border-2 bg-primary-600">
							<Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-6 h-6 text-white dark:text-slate-200" />
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="pt-1">
					<p class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-300">Repeat!</p>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400"></p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="relative">
						<Picture
							src={import('~/assets/images/profilePic.jpg')}
							class="mx-auto rounded-md"
							widths={[230, 460]}
							sizes="(max-width: 229px) 230px, (max-width: 459px) 460px"
							alt="Hero Image"
							aspectRatio={460/460}
							loading="eager"
							width={460}
							height={460}
						/>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
